{"id":15413,"date":"2022-12-15T06:29:21","date_gmt":"2022-12-14T23:29:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=15413"},"modified":"2022-12-15T06:29:21","modified_gmt":"2022-12-14T23:29:21","slug":"huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads.html\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo (Listing Ads)"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads.html\/#Hinh_anh_minh_hoa_khi_nguoi_dung_nhan_quang_cao\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads.html\/#Vi_tri_hien_thi\" title=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads.html\/#Nhung_loi_ich_cua_nha_quang_cao_khi_su_dung_quang_cao_tin_dang\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng:\">Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-tin-dang-tren-zalo-listing-ads.html\/#Cac_buoc_thiet_lap_quang_cao_tin_dang_tren_Zalo_Listing_Ads\" title=\"C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo (Listing Ads)\">C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo (Listing Ads)<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng Home &amp; Car (Listing Ads) tr\u00ean Zalo Ads nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ng\u00e0nh B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Xe qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tin \u0111\u0103ng t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u01a1n sau khi \u0111\u0103ng tin b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Zalo Home &amp; Car.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15415\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15415\" style=\"width: 2084px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15415 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form.jpeg\" alt=\"Huong-dan-quang-cao\" width=\"2084\" height=\"1250\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form.jpeg 2084w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form-300x180.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form-1024x614.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form-768x461.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form-1536x921.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ZAD_thumbnail_500x300_HDQC-form-2048x1228.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2084px) 100vw, 2084px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15415\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m 2 thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n: \u0110\u0103ng th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean Zalo Home &amp; Car t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u00a0v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hinh_anh_minh_hoa_khi_nguoi_dung_nhan_quang_cao\"><\/span>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15414\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15414\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15414 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Untitled-design-700x394-1.png\" alt=\"Hinh-anh-minh-hoa\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Untitled-design-700x394-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Untitled-design-700x394-1-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15414\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda tr\u00e3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Zalo khi nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Listing Ads<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vi_tri_hien_thi\"><\/span><strong>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo (Listing Ads) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Zalo Group nh\u01b0 New Feed v\u00e0 Zalo Network (Baomoi, Zing\u2026.)<\/p>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Zalo New Feed v\u00e0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Zalo<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15416\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15416\" style=\"width: 451px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15416 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/LANF.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-tren-zalo-new-feed\" width=\"451\" height=\"867\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/LANF.png 451w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/LANF-156x300.png 156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15416\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Zalo New Feed<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Zalo Network<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_loi_ich_cua_nha_quang_cao_khi_su_dung_quang_cao_tin_dang\"><\/span>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn 65 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo,<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Zalo kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 trang web b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u0103ng c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n l\u00ean Home &amp; Car sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u0103ng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m,<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chat v\u00e0 k\u1ebft b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ngay th\u00f4ng qua Zalo chat sau khi xem tin \u0111\u0103ng. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i,\u00a0<strong>ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng chat<\/strong>,\u00a0<strong>k\u1ebft b\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin nh\u1eafn h\u1ecfi mua t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng:<\/strong>\u00a0Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n b\u1eadt ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9\u00a0<strong>\u201cCho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1 nh\u1eafn tin\u201d\u00a0<\/strong>tr\u00ean Zalo<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng tin tr\u00ean Home &amp; Car v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tin \u0111\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_buoc_thiet_lap_quang_cao_tin_dang_tren_Zalo_Listing_Ads\"><\/span>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo (Listing Ads)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o vui l\u00f2ng xem th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch\u00a0<strong>t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:\u202f<\/strong>\u00a0Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng theo 2 c\u00e1ch:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15417\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-700x700-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-700x700-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-700x700-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-700x700-1-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15419\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-700x700-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-700x700-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-700x700-1-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-700x700-1-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch 1:\u00a0<\/strong>Truy c\u1eadp\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/ads.zalo.me\/client\/ads\/select-campaign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/ads.zalo.me\/client\/ads\/select-campaign<\/a>\u00a0nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Zalo Ads. Sau \u0111\u00f3 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u201cQu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng\u201d. N\u1ebfu t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n tin \u0111\u0103ng \u1edf Home &amp; Car, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u0103ng tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15418\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Listing-ads-2-700x307-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Listing-ads-2-700x307-1.jpg 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Listing-ads-2-700x307-1-300x132.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch 2:\u00a0<\/strong>V\u00e0o \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Zalo tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, truy c\u1eadp m\u1ee5c\u00a0<strong>Home &amp; Car<\/strong>\u00a0\u1edf m\u1ee5c\u00a0<strong>Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1<\/strong>, \u0111\u0103ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat \u201cB\u00e1n nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn \u201cT\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ngay\u201d.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2:\u00a0<\/strong>Sau khi thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u00f3m \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed cho qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tin \u0111\u0103ng c\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o tin \u0111\u0103ng, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o \u201c<strong>T\u1ea1o tin \u0111\u0103ng m\u1edbi<\/strong>\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng tin b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng tin d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eadt Zalo, v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c Kh\u00e1m Ph\u00e1, ch\u1ecdn Zalo Home &amp; Car r\u1ed3i \u0111\u0103ng tin.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3:<\/strong>\u00a0Sau khi ch\u1ecdn tin \u0111\u0103ng, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p><em>L\u01b0u \u00fd: Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc xem tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat\u202f<strong>G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong>\u202f\u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn BQT Zalo Ads ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 x\u00e9t duy\u1ec7t.\u202f Trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng ng\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy\u1ec7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15420\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15420\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15420 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Giay-phep-quang-cao-moi-700x276-1.png\" alt=\"Gui-duyet-quang-cao\" width=\"700\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Giay-phep-quang-cao-moi-700x276-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Giay-phep-quang-cao-moi-700x276-1-300x118.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15420\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t qu\u1ea3ng c\